des:
Wanderlust. Traveler’s itch. Road-trip-itis. Whatever you call it, Madison has the cure. 

Before your next visit to Madison, Wisconsin, ask Alexa for help planning your trip. Enable the Visit Madison skill, then invoke it by saying, "Alexa, Open Visit Madison." She'll ask you three questions, and depending on your answers, deliver a guide to Madison that suits your particular fancy.

Don't love everything on your list? Try the quiz again to suit your mood — you might get a different result.

Madison Seems Nice, doesn't it?
